                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-06-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 29, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>British Government concludes Camara can not remain at Port Said more than
                    twenty-four hours, except in case of necessity, and can not coal there if he has
                    coal enough to take him back to Cadiz, which appears to be the case.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hay.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
